---
// Burayı boş bırakıyoruz, hata riskini sıfırlıyoruz.
---

<html lang="tr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>iyibilgilernet | Hoş Geldiniz</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<h1>Hoş Geldiniz, <span class="text-gradient">iyibilgilernet</span></h1>
			<p class="subtitle">Güncel bilgiler, ipuçları ve hayatın içinden esintiler.</p>

			<!-- ÖNE ÇIKAN VİDEO BÖLÜMÜ -->
			<section class="video-container">
				<h2>Son Paylaşılan Video</h2>
				<div class="video-wrapper"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZuRrZ1Q-f3I?si=_vWvZfm2AMHmMSwj" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- SOSYAL MEDYA BUTONLARI -->
			<section class="social-links">
				<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@iyibilgilernet" target="_blank" class="btn youtube">YouTube</a>
				<a href="https://www.instagram.com/iyibilgilernet" target="_blank" class="btn instagram">Instagram</a>
				<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@iyibilgilernet" target="_blank" class="btn tiktok">TikTok</a>
			</section>
		</main>

		<style>
			:root {
				--accent: 124, 58, 237;
				--accent-gradient: linear-gradient(45deg, rgb(var(--accent)), #da62c4 30%, white 60%);
			}
			html {
				font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
				background-color: #13151a;
				color: white;
			}
			body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
			main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    width: 100%; /* Sabit genişlik yerine tam ekran yapalım */
    max-width: 800px; /* Ama çok da yayılmasın */
    box-sizing: border-box;
}
			h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2.2rem); /* Ekran küçüldükçe yazı da küçülür */
    word-wrap: break-word;
    white-space: normal; /* Harflerin alta kaymasını engeller, kelimeyi bütün tutar */
}
			.text-gradient {
				background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
				background-size: 400%;
				background-position: 0%;
			}
			.subtitle {
				font-size: 1rem;
				color: #a1a1a1;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			.video-container {
				background: #1e2029;
				padding: 15px;
				border-radius: 20px;
				border: 1px solid #333;
			}
			.video-wrapper {
				position: relative;
				padding-bottom: 56.25%;
				height: 0;
				overflow: hidden;
				border-radius: 12px;
			}
			.video-wrapper iframe {
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			.social-links {
				margin-top: 2rem;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 10px;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
			}
			.btn {
				padding: 8px 20px;
				border-radius: 50px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: white;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				transition: 0.2s;
			}
			.youtube { background: #cc0000; }
			.instagram { background: #c13584; }
			.tiktok { background: #010101; border: 1px solid #444; }
			.btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 0.9; }
		</style>
	</body>
</html>